{
  "stem": "1363.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The next morning when the train for, for Budapest arrived, he took them to the train, those four women.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they went back to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did know about any-- I only knew that she is not in the station where we arrived at, and that she's all right, so I was told.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now I took her haversack.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I thought to myself, well if she's not here, I am going to try to get back as well.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Completely on my own.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By that stage all my other aunties already somehow or other disappeared from the scene.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think the other two aunties who were with us from-- in the, in the brick factory, I think from the brick factory they somehow went back.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How it happened, I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I only know that they did not march with me anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, every station they have waited for us with a huge big, barrel, or whatever you want to call it, with soup, which they have put in roots of carrots or potatoes, and that's what they have given out to all these people.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But by the time it came to me, or towards the end or the middle of the-- of the 2,500, by that time it was only 2,000 because quite a few died on the way, or they shot or so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was-- I remember we ate something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I can't-- I only know that there was-- what-- oh, how can I translate it?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know what the pigs eat when you have all the food, the remnants put together in a-- in a-- Like a compost?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A compost sort of thing, it was dreadful.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we did eat something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I can't think.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
